frames.caption: A young girl with big, expressive eyes sits on a bed, gazing dreamily out the window. Her hair is styled in a messy bun, and she is wearing a cozy white sweater. A small stuffed animal sits beside her, adding a touch of warmth to the scene.
frames.description: The scene is set in a cozy bedroom with a large window overlooking a cityscape. The girl appears to be in a moment of peaceful contemplation, surrounded by the soft glow of the setting sun filtering through the window.

frames.caption: A young girl peacefully sleeps while hugging a plush teddy bear, bathed in the warm glow of a sunrise. She is nestled in bed, with a cityscape visible through the large window beside her.
frames.description: The scene depicts a serene morning setting in a cozy bedroom. The girl is resting comfortably, suggesting a sense of calm and security, while the city outside is softly illuminated by the early sunlight.
